rules:
• Server Goes LIVE After The Game Reaches 18 vs 18 Players.
  •  Fighting Is Allowed Over The Two Middle Obj. OR Center Obj. Whichever Applies.
  •  DO NOT Attack, Dig, Or IED HABs and/or FOBs.
  •  NO Armed Vehicles Are Allowed.
  •  Mortars Are Not Allowed; Smoke and H.E.
  •  Only One FOB And HAB Is Permitted.
  •  FOBs And HABs Placed On Capture Points Are Subject To Attack.
